lement" href="/documentation/tagLibrary/note">note</a>, <a href="/documentation/tagLibrary/orig">orig</a>, <a title="Show description of pad-element" href="/documentation/tagLibrary/pad">pad</a>, <a title="Show description of proport-element" href="/documentation/tagLibrary/proport">proport</a>, <a title="Show description of reg-element" href="/documentation/tagLibrary/reg">reg</a>, <a href="/documentation/tagLibrary/rest">rest</a>, <a title="Show description of restore-element" href="/documentation/tagLibrary/restore">restore</a>, <a title="Show description of sic-element" href="/documentation/tagLibrary/sic">sic</a>, <a href="/documentation/tagLibrary/space">space</a>, <a title="Show description of subst-element" href="/documentation/tagLibrary/subst">subst</a>, <a title="Show description of supplied-element" href="/documentation/tagLibrary/supplied">supplied</a>, <a title="Show description of tuplet-element" href="/documentation/tagLibrary/tuplet">tuplet</a>, <a title="Show description of unclear-element" href="/documentation/tagLibrary/unclear">unclear</a></p><h3>May occur within:</h3><p><a title="Show description of add-element" href="/documentation/tagLibrary/add">add</a>,
